<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.268152>
    dc:description "FIGURE 20. Cymbasoma bidentatum sp. nov., adult female. A) habitus, dorsal view; B) cephalic region, lateral view; C) same, dorsal view; D) urosome, dorsal view, triangular posterior processes arrowed; E) same, lateral view; F) same, showing fifth legs, ventral view; G) distal section of ovigerous spines. Scale bars: A = 200 µm, B – G = 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/268152/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.268153>
    dc:description "FIGURE 21. Cymbasoma bidentatum sp. nov., adult female. A) habitus, lateral view; B) right antennule, dorsal view; C) detail of process on first antennulary segment (arrowed); D) cephalic region, lateral view; E) third leg; F) urosome, lateral view, right fifth leg omitted to show anteroventral process on genital double-somite; G) same, showing fifth legs, ventral view. Scale bars: A = 200 µm, B, C = 50 µm, D – G = 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/268153/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

